node.text:
🖤🖤 Wow!!! 🖤🖤⁠
⁠
🖤On this day 5 years ago, April 16th, 2016, we opened our doors and poured our first beer. We couldn’t have made it this far without you all, and we truly feel humbled by your faithfulness and support. This past year has been difficult for everyone and we’ve had to adapt constantly, but y’all have shown up for us over and over. 🖤 We have grown and learned so much in these last 5 years and will continue to push ourselves to try new things. Let’s do another 5 my babiez! 😝🖤⁠
⁠
🖤 All Anniversary beers are online now! Head on over to www.theveilbrewing.com/anniversary. We can’t wait to see you and celebrate this special milestone. Again, thank you from the bottom of our hearts. 🙏 🖤

⌛️☠️⚰️🐈 ACT I-III 🐈⚰️☠️⌛️⠀⠀
⠀⠀
⌛️☠️⚰️🐈 The pinnacle of our spirit barrel aged high gravity program is finally ready. 🖤 Sleeping Forever Grand Cru is a blend of 1, 2, and 3 year old Buffalo Trace bourbon barrel aged Sleeping Forever. It has an exceptionally refined depth of barrel character and flavor that only comes with time and careful blending of different vintages. Sleeping Forever Grand Cru will only be released every 5 years and is packaged in matte black bottles, waxed dipped, black velvet labels, wrapped in a custom handkerchief, and laid to rest in special individual boxes with a faux ostrich skin exterior and red velvet interior. All you could ask for in a bourbon barrel aged Imperial Stout - layer upon layer of sweet tobacco, drippy/oily vanilla, melted dark chocolate, top-shelf bourbon, and balanced American oak. 13% ABV ⌛️☠️⚰️🐈⠀⠀

node.text: Please take a moment to watch this video and follow @richmondrestaurantsunited. What’s happening right now directly impacts our entire food and beverage community. Your favorite restaurants, bars, and breweries are all hurting right now. Some forced to furlough most of their staff, others not sure if they will ever reopen their doors. All of us are pivoting to try and do what we can to keep our lights on and our staff taken care of the best we can. Please consider donating and writing to our local and state government asking them for immediate action. Please be safe, take care of yourselves, and support as many local business you can. Most are offering to-go and delivery. Anything helps right now. 🖤 🖤 We will continue to offer outdoor to-go sales only from both our RVA and NFK taprooms Tues-Fri 1-7pm and Sat&Sun 12-6pm. Please check out our last post made earlier today for info about RVA deliveries too. We are hoping to offer NFK delivery starting next week. Also looking into other creative ways to get our cans and bottles into the hands of more Virginians and beyond. Please check out our webstore on our website(www.theveilbrewing.com) and consider purchasing a gift card for future use or some merchandise if possible. Every purchase made right now directly benefits our staff as we continue to find ways to work through these difficult times. Your continued support is greatly appreciated. 🖤

Dusty Roadz 🛣🌪⁠

Dusty Roadz is our Pale Ale brewed and dry-hopped with Citra, Citra Cryo and Nelson Sauvin hops! Popping out of the glass with dank tropical melon and light crispy crackers. Super crushable. We should make more pale ales. 😉 5.2% ABV. $14.00+tax/4pack.⁠

Dirt Nap⁴ 🐂 💤 ⁠
⁠
Dirt Nap⁴ is our Double IPA brewed with Galaxy, Citra, Mosaic, and Nelson! Extremely saturated flavors of sweet pineapple, canned peach juice, white grape, and soft papaya. 8.8% ABV. $20.00+tax/4pack. ⁠
⁠
Remain Bright ☀️👓 ⁠
⁠
Remain Bright is a brand new DIPA brewed with Strata, Mosaic, Citra, Sabro, and Nelson hops. A hoppy flavor ride of pungent fruit, grape skin, fresh apricot, and coconut cream.  8% ABV. $17.50+tax/4pack.⁠
⁠
No More Flowers 🚫💐🚫⁠
⁠
No More Flowers is our beloved Kölsch-inspired beer. Thirst quenching, beautiful, and crispy from 5 weeks of lagering with a distinct soft and delicate ester profile balanced by a light German Tettnang hop addition. 5.2% ABV. $12.00+tax/4pack. ⁠

⁠⁠⁠⁠
✌️RVA on Tuesday, 8/3🙅‍♂️⁠
🍺NFK on Wednesday, 8/4⛰⁠
⁠
❌IdontwanttoBU⁴🙅‍♂️⁠
⁠
IdontwanttoBU⁴ is the quadruple dry-hopped version of our Mosaic and Citra 0 IBU IPA. Blasted with a concentrated hop character of mango and honey sweetness. 6.9% ABV.⁠
⁠
✌️Valley of Peace⛰⁠
⁠
Valley of Peace is a brand new Double IPA brewed with Citra, Strata, plus New Zealand Cascade and Nelson. Quite the lineup of amazing hops. Drippy flavors of sweet passion fruit, mango, and honey dew melon. 8% ABV.⁠
⁠
🛡War in My Mind 🗣⁠
⁠
War in My Mind is a brand new Triple India Pale Ale brewed with a generous portion of flaked wheat, malted wheat, as well as raw wheat. Hopped with Mosaic, Mosaic Cryo, Galaxy and a touch of Columbus. Impressions of sugary, ripe, exotic produce with a touch of welcomed dankness. 11% ABV.⁠
⁠
❤️Never Never Again Again❤️⁠
⁠
Never Never Again Again is a Gose Ale with double raspberry purée. A raspberry purée bomb reminiscent of summer time push pops. 5.1% ABV.⁠
⁠
🦌 Schröderhaüst 🍺 ⁠
⁠
Schröderhaüst is a brand new Bavarian-inspired Wheat Ale aka Weissebier. Step mashed, and gently hopped with select German Noble hops, this beer is inspired by one of our favorite German brewers of this style. Extremely refreshing with lovely esters of banana and spice with the perfect touch of  effervescence, dryness, and subtle bitterness. 5.1% ABV.⁠
⁠
⁠
NO LIMITS. See you Tuesday for these!
